Class Game_Profile

  • java.lang.Object
    • Game_Structure.Game_Profile

  • public class Game_Profile
extends java.lang.Object
    Game_Profile Class is implemented as a Model class (Project is trying to approach to Model-view-controller design pattern) This class implemented as a data base for all View and Controller class.
    Author:
    Edward Wong - University of Canterbury SENG_201 15/05/2020

        Parameters:
        farmer_type - The type of farm in the range of 0 - 3
        farmer_name - Farmer name of player
        farm_name - Farm name selected by user
        farmer_energy - Farmer energy to perform action
        end_day - Farmer conntract end day (end game)
